underlying_goal: To correct the citations for password-locked models in a research paper.
primary_success: Correctly identifying that the password-locked models came from two separate sources (van der Weij et al. and Redwood/Greenblatt et al.) and adding the missing citation for the Redwood paper.
brief_summary: The user questioned the citations for password-locked models. The agent investigated and confirmed that the models came from two different sources, but only one was cited. The agent then found the missing Redwood Research paper, added it to the bibliography, updated the citation in the main text, and committed the fix.
